<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[اللَّوِي]</span>: ما يبس من البقل.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فَعِيلة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[ي]</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[اللَّوِيَّة]</span>: ما ذَخَرَتْه المرأةُ من طعامها، وجمعها لوايا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
